      • getParameterCitations

        public List<CICitationPropertyType> getParameterCitations()
        Gets the value of the parameterCitations property. <p> This accessor method returns a reference to the live list, not a snapshot. Therefore any modification you make to the returned list will be present inside the JAXB object. This is why there is not a <CODE>set</CODE> method for the parameterCitations property. <p> For example, to add a new item, do as follows: <pre> getParameterCitations().add(newItem); </pre> <p> Objects of the following type(s) are allowed in the list CICitationPropertyType
